{"questionId":"1251289","questionHtml":"<p>A horizontal force <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>F</mi></math> acts on a sphere. A horizontal resistive force <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>k</mi><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> acts on the sphere where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>v</mi></math> is the speed of the sphere and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>k</mi></math> is a constant. What is the terminal velocity of the sphere?</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msqrt><mfrac><mi>k</mi><mi>F</mi></mfrac></msqrt></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>k</mi><mi>F</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>F</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msqrt><mfrac><mi>F</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac></msqrt></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"1251289","referenceCode":"20N.1A.SL.TZ0.10","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"A horizontal force F acts on a sphere. A horizontal resistive force kv2 acts on the sphere where v is the speed of the sphere and k is a constant. What is the terminal velocity of ","paper":"1A","level":"SL","questionNumber":"10","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["A. Space, time and motion","A.2 Forces and momentum"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}